-- Finmeccanica's Ansaldo STS Says It's Monitoring for Possible Acquisitions
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-04-23T09:38:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/finmeccanica-s-ansaldo-sts-says-it-s-monitoring-for-possible-acquisitions.html

          
          
             Ansaldo STS SpA said it’s
monitoring for possible acquisitions of companies involved in
“complementary industrial and commercial activities,”
according to a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  
 The company may also consider stake purchases and said it
is “well positioned” to benefit from investment opportunities
“due to its strong financial situation.”  
          
          


  


        